Hemigrammus marginatus
(not Ellis): Géry, 1964: 27 , fig. 4 (photo in life), 32 ( Peru , Loreto , “surroundings of Iquitos”; specimen examined); Lüling, 1981: 175 (upper photo), 176 ( Peru , Ucayali , Pucallpa, “Weisswasserbach” at road to Tournavista; specimen not examined); Ortega & Vari, 1986: 8 (listed for Peru ; based on Géry, 1964 ); Bogotá-Gregory & Maldonado-Ocampo, 2006: 67 (listed, Amazon basin, Colombia ; see Discussion);
